/** varible: carbon monoxide,  source: anthropogenic, version: latest, year: 2020 **/

                import cdsapi

                c = cdsapi.Client()

                c.retrieve(
                    'cams-global-emission-inventories',
                    {
                        'version': 'latest',
                        'format': 'zip',
                        'variable': 'carbon_monoxide',
                        'source': 'anthropogenic',
                        'year': '2020',
                    },
                    'download.zip')
              
              
              
                    
EDGAR     http://edgar.jrc.ec.europa.eu/    
EDGAR is a multipurpose, independent, global database of anthropogenic emissions of greenhouse gases and air pollution on Earth. EDGAR provides independent emission estimates compared to what reported by European Member States or by Parties under the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC), using international statistics and a consistent IPCC methodology.
EDGAR provides both emissions as national totals and gridmaps at 0.1 x 0.1 degree resolution at global level, with yearly, monthly and up to hourly data.
 有不同国家不同年份 Fossil CO2 Share ，Gross Domestic Product Share ，Population Share 占 world 总数的比值。
 有不同国家不同年份 Greenhouse gases        由不同的Sector（e.g buildings , transports, power industry）           产生的数值和趋势图，可以以不同格式下载。
 有不同国家不同年份 Air and Toxic pollutant 由不同Sector（e.g buildings , transports, power industry, Agriculture) 产生的数值和趋势图，可以以不同格式下载。

